[Preventing salmonellosis in the kitchen remains a multifactorial process related to adequate cooking and appropriate kitchen hygiene and refrigeration.

The serotype of _S. enterica_ is not stated here nor is the number of individuals who ate the food, which could give us the attack rate of this cluster. - Mod.LL

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/3aDQ.]
